Type Guard:
-----------
1)  typeof -> can only test against string, number, boolean , symbol

if(typeof x === 'string'){

}

if(typeof x === 'string'|'number'){

}



2) instanceof => if(device instanceof phone)

3) User defined type guards:

interface Vehicle { numberOfWheels: number;}

function isVehicle(v:any):v is Vehicle{ //This is part is required
    return (<Vehicle>v).numberOfWheels !==undefined;
    //OR return layer.type === Enumtype.TEXT
}
